## Mendeley Reference Manager v2.136.0
 
We have:
 
- Fixed an issue where annotations made in Mendeley Desktop were not showing in Mendeley Reference Manager
- Fixed an issue where links inside a PDF would stop working
- Fixed the folder tree structure so it remains open in the same location when moving to the reader and back to the library
- Added the ability to import references using an ISBN
- Improved the performance of the library sync
- Added auto-suggestion for tags based on existing tags in the library
- Fixed an issue with cookies for users using "Sign in via your organization"
- Fixed an issue where author names wouldn't update after using DOI look-up

 
## Support

- If you encounter any problems using Mendeley or have questions to ask please [contact our support team](https://www.mendeley.com/contact-support/ "Contact support").
